page.title: 02A CATTERLINE BOY'S DAY
page.content: I get up in the morning at quarter to 8 and get dressed.I usually wear black cords, a blue shirt, white socks, a jumper and a pair of trainers. I have breakfast which is a cup of tea and two pieces of toast.I wash after that, then pack my school bag and bicycle to school.We have a play-time then we start school.First thing is to get changed into our shorts then we get a gym teacher for 45 minutes. Then we have a play_time with a tuck shop for 15 minutes, after that we do written work like mathematics, English, history and geography. Then at half past 3 I bicycle home.If I have homework I do it then. I watch television till five o' clock which is tea time.Then at 9 0' clock I go to bed.
